# Project 1
Make a temperature sensor using Arduino Uno and 16x2 LCD.
The following components are used:
1. Arduino UNO
2. 16x2 LCD
3. Jumper
4. Bread board
5. Sensor LM35

Make a series like the following picture.

Open the Arduino IDE software, then connect the Arduino Uno to the PC via the USB port.

Send a program that I have made. Please upload the program using CTRL + U or click the upload icon.

Wait until the program upload process is complete if there is the word "Done Uploading"

Don't forget to subscribe to my blog www.duinoelektronik.blogspot.com and follow IG @duinogram

Thanks
